Jot does not currently use analytics tracking.

OR

Jot may use basic analytics or diagnostics to understand app performance, crashes, and feature reliability. This is used to improve the app and is not used for advertising.

7. Your choices

You can control the information you enter into Jot.

You can delete food logs or app data using features available in the app, where provided. You can also delete the app from your device to remove locally stored app data.

If you have sent feedback or diagnostic information and want to ask about deletion, contact us using the details below.

8. Children

Jot is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

9. Changes to this policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make significant changes, we will update the effective date above.

